NB. Create a multidimensional matrix representing an all-encompassing grid
OmniSpace =: i. 2 3 4 5  NB. A 4-Dimensional universe

NB. Define an omnipotent modifier function (multiplies everything everywhere)
OmniModify =: *&2 

NB. Apply it to the infinite rank of the space
Omniverse =: OmniModify OmniSpace
